<div id="pf32" class="pf w2 h6" data-page-no="32"><div class="pc pc32 w2 h6"><img class="bi x0 y0 w3 h7" alt="" src="bg32.png"/><div class="t m72 x43 h4a y45e ff1 fs26 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What Adventists Believe </div><div class="t m226 x41 h17 y1c8 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">During the third and fourth quarters of 1988, Sabbath Schools </div><div class="t m51d x60 h17 y665 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">around the world will turn temporarily from the Bible book cur-</div><div class="t m49f x60 h17 y666 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">riculum we have been studying. In order to revitalize our under-</div><div class="t m259 x60 h17 y1ca ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">standing of the fundamental beliefs of the Seventh-day Adventist </div><div class="t me7 x60 h17 y1cb ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Church, we will study one of the 27 statements of belief each Sab-</div><div class="t mbf x60 h17 y667 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bath over a two-quarter period. </div><div class="t m3ae x41 h17 y307 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">But there is more to this unique approach than reviewing our </div><div class="t m1da x60 h17 y668 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beliefs. Not only will you become more familiar with the teachings </div><div class="t m51e x60 h17 y669 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of your church but you also will be learning how to share your </div><div class="t m14f x60 h17 y66a ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beliefs with those who wish to know more about them. </div><div class="t m20a x41 h17 y1d0 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Watch for additional information that will give you guidance on </div><div class="t m51f x60 h17 y66b ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">how to combine your study of these lessons with supplemental out-</div><div class="t m15a x60 h17 y1d3 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reach tools such as doctrinal tracts, books, Bible lessons, and mis-</div><div class="t m1fa x60 h17 y66c ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sionary literature. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.0000